java.lang.Object
clinic.cs213project3.model.clinic.Timeslot
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Timeslot extends Object implements Comparable<Timeslot>
The general structure of a timeslot for the clinic. Clinic stores twelve timeslots initially.
